    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp shifts, complemented by a chassis that has received essential rear subframe reinforcement and updated bushings to maintain structural rigidity. It retains its factory-tuned suspension geometry, offering the precise feedback and 50/50 weight distribution the platform is known for. With the rod bearings serviced and the Variable M Differential Lock operating flawlessly, this M3 is ready for the technical driver seeking peak analog performance and an 8,000 RPM redline.",
