      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a stunning example of refined luxury and Japanese engineering. Finished in a sophisticated Deep Blue Mica, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the Parchment leather interior has been meticulously cared for; the seats are supple and free of tears, and the cabin remains fresh as a strictly non-smoker vehicle. All electronic features, including the premium navigation system, power liftgate, and heated/ventilated seating, function perfectly. Mechanically, this SUV is in great shape, backed by a consistent service history. We recently performed a multi-point inspection, confirming the engine runs smoothly, the brakes are responsive, and the Michelin tires have significant tread remaining. It is a reliable, comfortable cruiser that offers the premium experience of a high-end SUV without the new-car price tag.",
