    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and the occasional road trip. It shows a little bit of love from regular use, but it\u2019s still looking sharp and runs beautifully! If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
