      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies to deliver a sharp, linear throttle response. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a Vanos system overhaul, ensuring the chassis and valvetrain remain resilient under load. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the car exhibits minor cosmetic wear consistent with an enjoyed driver\u2019s car, its mechanical integrity and performance envelope remain exceptionally tight.",
